      "text": "The two datasets are merged to increase both coverage and domain balance."
    },
    {
      "id": "Q44",
      "page": 4,
      "dimension": "output_ontology",
      "text": "To ensure compatibility, the tag set is harmonised by merging the GPE and LOC categories into a single location label, while retaining PER, ORG, and MISC unchanged."
